<emphasis box="[703,778,188,213]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="181">πλατύς</emphasis>
(platy-, “flat”) and 
<emphasis box="[1004,1081,188,213]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="181">γνάθος</emphasis>
(gnatha, “jaw”) in reference to its strongly flattened mandible.
</paragraph>
